  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128030/extras/21e7ee2d81fa59f1f5de2319710b8227.avif?t=1663009299\" width=600 height=83 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the game</h2>This is a 3D platform control game. The gameplay is using a mind twisting method to control a spaceship to suck away the animals on the platform to complete the level task.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Background</h2>You have a mission to carry animals to a zoo. However, a sleepy thought slipped into your mind later discovered all animals have escaped on the way. There is one thing, you are controlling a thing that looks like a spaceship. And you saw your green arms, that doesn't look human at all! Catch the animals!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Control</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128030/extras/cbba690f64540836b52161e8e6a8928d.poster.avif?t=1663009299\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128030/extras/cbba690f64540836b52161e8e6a8928d.webm?t=1663009299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128030/extras/cbba690f64540836b52161e8e6a8928d.mp4?t=1663009299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Left Front - LT / Right Front - RT<br></li><li>Left Back - LB / Right Back - RB</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128030/extras/0e79f4f6173da2a38a4e009142f3ec25.poster.avif?t=1663009299\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128030/extras/0e79f4f6173da2a38a4e009142f3ec25.webm?t=1663009299\" type=\"video/webm; c